.vscode/**
.vscode-test/**
src/**
.gitignore
.yarnrc
vsc-extension-quickstart.md
**/tsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json
**/biome.json
**/*.map
**/*.ts
# `out/extension.js` is the bundled output of `esbuild.mjs`. All
# runtime dependencies (`vscode-languageclient` and its transitive
# tree) are inlined into that single file — `node_modules/` is
# irrelevant at install time and would only inflate the .vsix.
node_modules/**
esbuild.mjs
bun.lock
*.vsix
